<AbstractNarration>This workshop takes Alaska Native students attending the College of Rural Alaska to an international forum to present their own research on arctic economies, self-government arrangements, and environmental management practices.  They will meet other students, faculty and staff from circumpolar universities and establish a researech network for indigenous students in the arctic.</AbstractNarration>
